desc: The Ellipse element is used to draw an ellipse.

x.desc: The x location of the center of the ellipse relative to the registration point of the parent display object (in pixels).

y.desc: The y location of the center of the ellipse relative to the registration point of the parent display object (in pixels).

width.desc: The width of the ellipse (in pixels).

height.desc: The height of the ellipse (in pixels).
